Case called at 9:22am [mo]
Defendant Jackie L Wackerman in court with Attorney Teri M. Strohschein.   ADA Jeffrey Shock appears for the State of Wisconsin.
ADA Shock verifies victim rights compliance.

Victim, Teresa Wackerman makes a statement to the Court

Maximum penalties recited; Constitutional rights reviewed; plea of "Guilty" entered; factual basis stipulated; the Court accepts the plea, finds Defendant guilty, and orders Judgment of Conviction entered.

--to undergo any treatment or therapy as deemed appropriate by the Agent
--no dangerous weapons in the household (kitchen knifes may remain in household)
--not to refer to Teresa Wackerman as any demeaning or defacing terms
--to submit DNA sample to Sheriff upon demand
--to pay costs of $243  plus the $200 DNA surcharge
--to pay $100 Domestic Abuse surcharge

Days credit for time already served:  0  days
recess: 9:42am

The Court appoints Attorney Strohschein//repayment order of $30 a month starting 08-24-2015
